GMimeParserWarning = enum
  GMIME_WARN_DUPLICATED_HEADER = 1, GMIME_WARN_DUPLICATED_PARAMETER = 2,
  GMIME_WARN_UNENCODED_8BIT_HEADER = 3, GMIME_WARN_INVALID_CONTENT_TYPE = 4,
  GMIME_WARN_INVALID_RFC2047_HEADER_VALUE = 5,
  GMIME_WARN_MALFORMED_MULTIPART = 6, GMIME_WARN_TRUNCATED_MESSAGE = 7,
  GMIME_WARN_MALFORMED_MESSAGE = 8, GMIME_CRIT_INVALID_HEADER_NAME = 100,
  GMIME_CRIT_CONFLICTING_HEADER = 101, GMIME_CRIT_CONFLICTING_PARAMETER = 102,
  GMIME_CRIT_MULTIPART_WITHOUT_BOUNDARY = 103,
  GMIME_WARN_INVALID_PARAMETER = 201, GMIME_WARN_INVALID_ADDRESS_LIST = 202,
  GMIME_CRIT_NESTING_OVERFLOW = 300, GMIME_WARN_PART_WITHOUT_CONTENT = 301,
  GMIME_CRIT_PART_WITHOUT_HEADERS_OR_CONTENT = 302
GMimeParserWarningFunc = proc (offset: gint64; errcode: GMimeParserWarning;
                               item: cstring; user_data: pointer)
GMimeRfcComplianceMode = enum
  GMIME_RFC_COMPLIANCE_LOOSE, GMIME_RFC_COMPLIANCE_STRICT
